com.facebook.litho.drawable

Class ComparableIntIdDrawable

  • java.lang.Object
    • Drawable
      • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableDrawable
        • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableDrawableWrapper
          • com.facebook.litho.drawable.ComparableIntIdDrawable

  • public class ComparableIntIdDrawable
extends ComparableDrawableWrapper
    A comparable implementation for drawables where an explicit int identifier is compared to test for equivalence in isEquivalentTo(ComparableDrawable). Use this implementation for trivial cases where the number of drawables are discrete and finite. An example: 
    
  onCreateLayout(ComponentContext c, @State Day day) {

    Drawable drawable = getDrawableForDay(day);
    int id = day.ordinal(); // Day in an enum

    return Text.create(c)
      .text(day)
      .background(
        ComparableIntIdDrawable.create(drawable, id)
      )
      .build();
  }
